      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i just finished changing the brake pads on my 2018 camry but now when i pull out of the driveway i hear this really loud high pitched squealing noise. i dont think its the pads themselves since they are brand new. could it be a sensor or is the caliper stuck or something? help",
